      • initialize

        public void initialize​(java.net.URL url,
                       java.util.ResourceBundle resourceBundle)
        Handle the initialization of the main stage
        Specified by:
        initialize in interface javafx.fxml.Initializable
        Parameters:
        url - the url
        resourceBundle - the ResourceBundle I ran into several issues during development that lead me to implementing the Initializable pattern. This allowed me to populate some initial parts and products and speed up the development feedback loop. I also leveraged this method to apply listeners to simplify things like search.
